long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Schedule Aretex meetings directly from Google Calendar

Participants can schedule Aretex meetings directly from Google Calendar by using the Aretex Meet Extension. You can call a meeting now or plan one for later with the touch of a button. The invitee receives a Google Calendar invitation with the meeting URL and details, making it simple for them to join.

Aretex Meet Extension allows you to:
•  Start an instant meeting
•  Schedule a meeting
•  Schedule a meeting for other
